DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr"><b><b>Prepare for Passover this year - body and so
 ul</b></b></p><p><b><b><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://cbssf.
 shulcloud.com/form/cbs-makor-or-pesach5786&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&a
 mp\;ust=1771363476872869&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1pqJe5D4z9eCv6rM9dY4PK" target="_bl
 ank">Register here!</a></b></b></p><p>Join Makor Or this March for in-depth
  preparation for Passover through meditation\, learning\, and community.</p
 ><p><b><b>What We&#39\;re Offering:</b></b></p><ul><li><b><b>Two Tuesday Ev
 ening Sessions</b></b> – March 10 &amp\; 17\, 6:30-8 PM Pacific</li></ul><p
 >The Tuesday meetings will begin with a sit and include teachings and discu
 ssions led by Norman Fischer and R. Dorothy Richman. Each participant will 
 be encouraged to meet with a hevruta\, a study partner\, once a week\, outs
 ide of our meetings. </p><ul><li><b><b>Sunday All Day Retreat</b></b> – Mar
 ch 22\, 10 AM-5 PM Pacific</li></ul><p>All programs available both in-perso
 n at Congregation Beth Sholom (San Francisco) and on Zoom.</p><p>Committing
  to learning and practice in community will deepen your understanding and e
 xperience of the Passover holiday. All are encouraged and welcome to join u
 s\, regardless of prior experience with Judaism or meditation.</p><p><b><b>
 Pricing:</b></b></p><ul><li>Sunday retreat (in-person): $54</li><li>Tuesday
  sessions (in-person): $18 per session or both</li><li>All programs on Zoom
 : $36 flat rate (includes retreat + both Tuesday sessions)</li></ul><p>Our 
 community continues to be generous and help sponsor those who have a financ
 ial hardship to participate. Please reach out to me directly  (<a href="mai
 lto:rabbirichman@bethsholomsf.org" target="_blank">rabbirichman@bethsholoms
 f.org</a>) if you would like to join us and need some financial help.</p><p
 ><b><b>Schedule at a Glance:</b></b></p><ul><li>Tuesday\, March 10: 6:30-8 
 PM (follows Mincha)</li><li>Tuesday\, March 17: 6:30-8 PM (follows Mincha)<
 /li><li>Sunday\, March 22: 10 AM-5 PM</li></ul>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T212446Z
