DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T210000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260312T210000
DTSTAMP:20260310T152201
CREATED:20260205T000927Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T232227Z
UID:10001078-1773262800-1773349200@magnes.berkeley.edu
SUMMARY:Big Give 2026
DESCRIPTION:WRITE YOUR STORY IN BERKELEY’S STARS \nUC Berkeley’s Magnes Collection of Jewish Art and Life is a vibrant constellation of brilliant minds and shining ideas\, from transformative learning experiences in the museum to groundbreaking collections-based research. This BIG GIVE\, you can add fresh sparkle to that constellation. Each gift is a glimmering star\, a mark of gratitude for what Magnes means to you. We invite you to be that light to empower this extraordinary community by donating to the Magnes and being a part of UC Berkeley’s biggest fundraising event of the year! \nDonate to the Magnes Annual Fund\nDonate to the Magnes Signature Event Fund\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nYour dedication has a direct impact on the incredible exhibitions and programs that make UC Berkeley’s Magnes a beacon of Jewish art and culture in the Bay Area and beyond. Year after year\, Big Give powers us to thrive as a space for gathering\, teaching\, learning\, and creative expression. \n\n\n\nDon’t miss the chance to multiply your impact with our Big Match Challenge! Magnes supporter Vallery Feldman will contribute $2\,500 once 10 individual donors like you make a gift to the NEW Magnes Signature Event Fund during Big Give! This challenge match ends at 9pm on Thursday\, March 12. \n\n\n\nThis year\, be the light that illuminates the museum’s path forward. It is your generosity that helps Berkeley’s stars\, like the Magnes\, shine their brightest and donate to the Magnes! \n\n\n\nBig Give is an online fundraising tradition that began in 2014\, giving you and the entire Cal community  —  alumni\, parents\, students\, faculty\, staff\, and friends  —  the chance to come together to support your favorite schools and programs. Now celebrating its 11th year\, this annual day of giving allows you to amplify your generosity through awareness and contest prizes. \n\n\n\nBig Give starts at 9 p.m. PDT on Wednesday\, March 11\, and continues through 9 p.m. PDT on Thursday\, March 12\, 2026. \n\n\n\nVisit BigGive.berkeley.edu today and discover all the ways you can be the light. \n \nUse #CalBigGive and #TheMagnes on social media to show your Big Give support\, put the Magnes on the leaderboard\, and help us earn contest prizes and matching funds. \nThe Magnes BIG GIVE Page
URL:https://magnes.berkeley.edu/program/big-give-2026/
LOCATION:Magnes Collection of Jewish Life and Art\, 2121 Allston Way\, Berkeley\, CA\, 94720\, United States
CATEGORIES:Big Give
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://magnes.berkeley.edu/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Magnes_BigGive26_email1_16-9.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Magnes Collection of Jewish Art and Life":MAILTO:magnes@berkeley.edu
END:VEVENT
