SUMMARY:Kehilla Sings!
DESCRIPTION:Join Hazzan Shulamit and Musical Prayer Leader Julie Nesnansky to circle around and sing together!  As the month of Nisan and Pesach approaches\, we’ll focus on songs of Love and Resistance\, including chants emerging from the Singing Resistance movement in Minneapolis and locally\, too. Let’s bring our voices\, bodies\, and spirits together–  everyone’s welcome\, songsheets are provided.  Bring layers for warmth as we gather under the stars!\n\nOutside in the Courtyard (masks optional)
