SUMMARY:ONLINE ONLY: Living in the Presence Monthly Book Group
DESCRIPTION:Join us in reading Rabbi Burt Jacobson’s (z”l*) book Living in the Presence: A Personal Quest for the Baal Shem Tov. We will gather online monthly on the fourth Sundays from 4 to 5 pm to discuss a section\, and work our way through the book. This month we will be discussing chapters 19-20. The book is available for purchase here. Each gathering is a drop in space – feel free to read just the chapters that are being discussed and join in even if you aren’t reading the whole book sequentially. Join here.  \n*z”l stands for zichrono livracha\, May his memory be a blessing.
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/online-only-living-in-the-presence-monthly-book-group-12/
END:VEVENT
