UID:18462-1774378800-1774382400@jcceastbay.org
SUMMARY:Empower Yourself Against Antisemitism on Social Media
DESCRIPTION:The JCC East Bay is partnering with the organization Fighting Online Antisemitism to present a workshop to empower teens in online spaces. \nTeens and parents will learn skills such as: \n\nBeing able to spot antisemitism online\nKnowing when to engage and when to back off to guard your mental health\nHow to report antisemitism in ways that will actually get it taken down\n\nThe workshop will go over how to report antisemitism in such a way that it gets taken seriously by social media sites. We want all participants to be able to leave the workshop with new skills in their tool belt. \nThis workshop will take place online. \nPURCHASE TICKETS HERE
URL:https://jcceastbay.org/events/empower-yourself-against-antisemitism-on-social-media/
LOCATION:CA
CATEGORIES:Jewish Life,Youth & Teens
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://jcceastbay.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Empower-Yourself-Against-Antisemitism-on-Social-Media.jpg
END:VEVENT
