SUMMARY:VIRTUAL – Morning Meditation Sit
DESCRIPTION:A meditation sit led by Rabbi Dev Noily. Join us for sitting practice\, framed by the weekly Torah portion and the season in Jewish time. \nWednesday & Friday mornings on Zoom \nZoom room opens at 7:50am\, short teaching at 7:55am\, silent sit from 8:00-8:30am\, followed by mourner’s kaddish and time to share about loved ones lost. Ends by or before 9am. You’re invited to come for all or part\, and to join or leave at any time. \nJoin us here! Look for the password to join Meditation in the Kehilla Weekly Email.
URL:https://kehillasynagogue.org/event/virtual-morning-meditation-sit-52/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Zoom
CATEGORIES:Community,Feature on Home Page
