SUMMARY:“Our Class”
DESCRIPTION:Opening night of award-winning play about a wartime massacre of Jews by their neighbors in a small Polish village. Through April 5. Talkbacks March 29 after 2 p.m. performance with descendants of Jedwabne pogrom\, moderated by director Igor Golyak\, and April 3 after 7:30 p.m. performance with Golyak and Carey Perloff. $68 and up.
