UID:74obg2dgfalfvvvmff4g3bh89u@google.com
CREATED:20260310T193645Z
DESCRIPTION:<h2><b>Forever Remembered – An Immersive Sound Installation for
  Yom HaShoah</b></h2><p><b>Date:</b> Monday\, April 13\, 2026</p><p><b>Time
 :</b> 12:00 p.m. – 6:00 p.m. (Sound Installation &amp\; Hall of Remembrance
 )</p><p><b>Location:</b> JCC San Francisco\, 3200 California St\, San Franc
 isco</p><p><b>Cost:</b> Free\; Registration encouraged</p><p><b>Description
 :</b> Join the JFCS Holocaust Center and our community partners for <i>Fore
 ver Remembered</i>\, a powerful new community memorial experience honoring 
 the six million Jewish lives lost during the Holocaust.</p><p>Building on t
 he sacred tradition of the "Reading of Names\," this year’s commemoration f
 eatures an immersive sound installation by Bay Area artist Forest Reid. Thr
 oughout the afternoon\, the Hall of Remembrance will be transformed into a 
 space for deep listening and reflection. Visitors will encounter a continuo
 us soundscape of community voices—neighbors\, descendants\, and students—re
 ading the names of victims from our local archives\, weaving together a col
 lective act of remembrance.</p><p><b>The Experience Includes:</b></p><ul><l
 i><p><b>A Living Soundscape:</b> Listen to the names of family and communit
 y members read by the voices of today.</p></li><li><p><b>Space for Reflecti
 on:</b> Opportunities for candle-lighting and personal meditation.</p></li>
 <li><p><b>Memorial Books:</b> Engage with <i>Yizkor</i> (memorial) books co
 ntaining the names of those honored in the project.</p></li></ul><p><b>Add 
 Your Voice:</b> <i>Forever Remembered</i> is a living memorial that grows t
 hrough your participation. We invite you to record yourself reading names f
 rom the Holocaust Center’s archives or your own family history to be includ
 ed in the installation.</p><p><b><a href="https://forms.office.com/Pages/Re
 sponsePage.aspx?id=CBcP12OKdk-3fVvCFueV9Zfn4Y_cnudGsNmf7HwX08NURFdaNDBZMVdQ
 UE81VFY3UFVEMkVPUjFCMS4u">Register to Attend or Submit a Voice Recording</a
 ></b></p><p><i>Presented by the JFCS Holocaust Center in partnership with t
 he JCCSF\, Congregation Beth Sholom\, Congregation Emanu-El\, Congregation 
 Sha’ar Zahav\, and Congregation Sherith Israel.</i></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260310T193824Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Yom HaShoa: "Forever Remembered" with SF Holocaust Center
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
