SUMMARY:Yom HaShoah: Tales from a Survivor's Descendant
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a survivor testimony from Ezra the grandchild of two Holocaust survivors Carl Rosner who survived both Kristallnacht and Buchenwald and Frieda Zeidschnur Rosner\, who survived the Vilnius Ghetto. \nThe first 45 minutes will be dedicated to Ezra giving his grandparents testimony and the rest of the event will be a talkback and guided discussion. \nCheck out our other event in this series a workshop on dealing with antisemitism on social media. \nPresented in partnership with Jewish Family and Children’s Holocaust Center \nREGISTER HERE TO ATTEND
