SUMMARY:Hausner Spring Benefit 2026: Celebrating Our 36th Anniversary
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we celebrate 36 years of joyful learning\, curiosity\, and community at Gideon Hausner Jewish Day School. This milestone gathering will bring together alumni\, families\, students\, faculty\, and friends on campus to honor our past and look forward to the future. \nEnjoy an evening of connection\, stories\, and celebration. All are welcome — we can’t wait to celebrate with you!
