DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Tot Shabbat with Dale Kleisley\, Director of Early Ch
 ildhood Education and Family Engagement and musical guests!\n \nOur bi-mont
 hly Tot Shabbat service is designed and created especially for children age
 d 5 and under and their families. (Siblings are welcome too!). Join us as w
 e share stories\, sing songs and recite prayers together. \n\nWHEN: 1st & 3
 rd Saturdays\, 10:30 a.m. - 11:30p.m.\nWHERE: Congregation Beth Sholom - Ch
 apel
