SUMMARY:J Street Policy Inaugural Policy Center Symposium
DESCRIPTION:Please join us on October 18 for the inaugural J Street Policy Center Symposium in the Bay Area. This event will bring together the best experts to discuss the struggle for peace and democracy in Israel and here\, alongside elected officials and local community leaders. More details to come very soon!
